        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/glenn_l_e_v_i_n_e/{size}/428_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-12-07T16:43:09.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Uncorked a bottle last night and it was too juicy, inky still at the two hour mark.  At 4-5 hours the wine softened and became lovely and more nuanced.  I paid ~ $45/btl and look forward to what\u2019s left of the case.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/e/b/ebbefe1b76ea042f3f4880230b82a1a34b03d227.jpeg\" alt=\"B28E374F-44A8-4744-8794-B3C3AD5298A1.jpeg\" data-base62-sha1=\"xDvp84Zk0AwhgVTLkUJErddA0hV\" width=\"1536\" height=\"3004\"></p>",
