        "created_at": "2019-12-07T17:16:51.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"19889\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Uncorked a bottle last night and it was too juicy, inky still at the two hour mark.  At 4-5 hours the wine softened and became lovely and more nuanced.  I paid ~ $45/btl and look forward to what\u2019s left of the case.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nB28E374F-44A8-4744-8794-B3C3AD5298A1.jpeg</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Good for you Glenn.</p>\n<p>BTW have you been out to see any of the buildup to the Sheep Ranch at Bandon?  Heading out next year after a hiatus from Bandon following 7 straight years.</p>",
