        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-12-07T17:31:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"19889\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Uncorked a bottle last night and it was too juicy, inky still at the two hour mark.  At 4-5 hours the wine softened and became lovely and more nuanced.  I paid ~ $45/btl and look forward to what\u2019s left of the case.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I opened one a week ago, too. Much more integrated than it was on release, I think it will really begin to hit is plateau in another five or six years.</p>",
